<div id="wikicontent"><div class="page"><p>There are 136 artifacts. The following is a summary of the frequency of each power; no account is taken of the rarity or depth if items, this is purely a numerical count.<h4 id="s2_1">Curses</h4><ul><li>Permanent Curses: 2<li>Heavy Curses: 9<li>Light Curses: 10</ul><ul><li>Reduces experience: 5<li>Aggravates nearby creatures: 19</ul><h4 id="s2_2">Elemental Powers</h4><ul><li>Branded with Poison: 8<li>Branded with Acid: 5<li>Branded with Lightning: 4<li>Branded with Fire: 17<li>Branded with Cold: 12</ul><ul><li>Resistance to Poison: 15<li>Resistance to Acid: 37<li>Resistance to Lightning: 33<li>Resistance to Fire: 49<li>Resistance to Cold: 43</ul><ul><li>Immunity to Acid: 4<li>Immunity to Lightning: 4<li>Immunity to Fire: 5<li>Immunity to Cold: 3</ul><h4 id="s2_3">Resistances</h4><ul><li>Paralysis: 38<li>Nexus: 11<li>Confusion: 13<li>Blindness: 13<li>Chaos: 13<li>Nether: 12<li>Experience Draining: 10<li>Sound: 8<li>Disenchantment: 14<li>Light: 22<li>Darkness: 28<li>Shards: 6<li>Fear: 27</ul><h4 id="s2_4">Stats</h4><ul><li>Increases Strength: 43<li>Increases Intelligence: 27<li>Increases Wisdom: 29<li>Increases Dexterity: 42<li>Increases Constitution: 33<li>Increases Charisma: 23</ul><ul><li>Sustains Strength: 8<li>Sustains Intelligence: 5<li>Sustains Wisdom: 6<li>Sustains Dexterity: 8<li>Sustains Constitution: 10<li>Sustains Charisma: 5</ul><h4 id="s2_5">Slays</h4><ul><li>Slay Evil Creatures: 26<li>Slay Dragons: 8<li>Slay Demons: 12<li>Slay Undead: 12<li>Slay Giants: 12<li>Slay Trolls: 27<li>Slay Orcs: 27<li>Slay Animals: 17</ul><ul><li><b>Slay</b> Dragons: 11<li><b>Slay</b> Demons: 5<li><b>Slay</b> Undead: 5</ul><h4 id="s2_6">Abilities</h4><ul><li>Endows the wielder with telepathy: 10<li>Enables the wielder to see invisible creatures: 47<li>Increases speed: 30<li>Allows more blows to be struck each combat turn: 5<li>Allows more shots to be fired each combat turn: 2<li>Increases the damage multiplier for missiles: 4<li>Speeds the regaining of hit points and spell points: 18<li>Illuminates the wielder&#39;s surroundings: 24<li>Confers or extends infravision: 8<li>Improves stealth: 16<li>Reduces damage from falls: 11<li>Reduces the need for food: 17<li>Improves searching: 9<li>Improves digging: 5<li>IMPACT: 1</ul><ul><li>Is blessed: 12</ul></div></div>

